 A man, Sani Garba, 32, has been arrested by police for allegedly raping a 60-year-old woman. Garba reportedly broke into the woman’s room in Suleja and forcefully had sexual intercourse with her. Garba said he was attracted by the victim’s shaking buttocks and was pushed by the devil to forcefully have her. “Whenever I see her, her buttocks used to attract me and I could not resist her. I cannot get over myself whenever I see her.“    